00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:48,680
 evo,

453
00:16:48,680 --> 00:16:50,620
 nisam jednostavno mogla prihvatiti

454
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:51,420
 da je ruka tako,

455
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:53,260
 a najbolnije je bilo od svega,

456
00:16:53,260 --> 00:16:54,700
 što su mi u agenciji rekli,

457
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:57,020
 da se okrene malo,

458
00:16:57,020 --> 00:16:57,840
 s lijeve strane,

459
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:58,860
 tako da na snimanju

460
00:16:58,860 --> 00:16:59,860
 se ne skuži,

461
00:16:59,860 --> 00:17:01,420
 da zapravo moja ruka desna,

462
00:17:01,420 --> 00:17:02,480
 imam čak jednu sliku

463
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,580
 kod sam danas pokazivala

464
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:04,640
 klincima u mobitelu,

465
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:05,880
 ta lukoske osjećanja,

466
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:06,440
 da,

467
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:08,520
 ja sam onda u tom semu rekla,

468
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:08,720
 pa,

469
00:17:09,080 --> 00:17:10,320
 nima uopće stalo,

470
00:17:10,320 --> 00:17:11,820
 nije nikom stalo,

471
00:17:11,820 --> 00:17:13,300
 pa čak ni mene nije bilo stalo,

472
00:17:13,300 --> 00:17:15,220
 ali sam znala da ne želim više tako,

473
00:17:15,220 --> 00:17:17,160
 ali opet zaražujem užasno puno,

474
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,480
 i kako ću se to prekinut, ne?

475
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:21,780
 I onda se desio taj vrlo znakoviti trenutak

476
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:22,520
 u mom životu,

477
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:23,000
 ja bih rekla,

478
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:23,960
 božnja intervencija,

479
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:25,580
 on je dopustio da se meni desi,

480
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:26,200
 možda ni,

481
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,600
 jer je znao da će me tako

482
00:17:27,600 --> 00:17:29,140
 jedino moći malo ošamariti,

483
00:17:29,140 --> 00:17:30,220
 da mi kaže ono,

484
00:17:30,220 --> 00:17:30,780
 daj halo,

485
00:17:30,780 --> 00:17:33,140
 šta radiš ti sa sobom,

486
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:34,080
 sa svojim životom?

487
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:35,800
 To je bilo badnje veče,

488
00:17:35,800 --> 00:17:36,780
 ja budistica,

489
00:17:36,780 --> 00:17:39,400
 spremam se na izlazak večernji,

490
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:40,580
 i moj cimer,

491
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:42,460
 znači dečko koji žive u stanu do mene,

492
00:17:42,460 --> 00:17:42,920
 me zove,

493
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:43,940
 kuca mi na vrata,

494
00:17:43,940 --> 00:17:44,480
 i kaže,

495
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,840
 ti se spremaš,

496
00:17:45,840 --> 00:17:46,200
 ja kažem,

497
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,440
 daj idem van na večeru,

498
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,500
 i sad ne znam gdje idem,

499
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:49,600
 on kaže,

500
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:51,600
 ja htjela sam te pitati da ideš sa mnom na misu,

501
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:52,500
 ja kažem,

502
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:53,660
 daj ti nisi normalan,

503
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:54,700
 pa ja sam budistica,

504
00:17:54,800 --> 00:17:56,360
 kaj ću ja na misi u crkvi,

505
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:56,800
 halo,

506
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:58,580
 onda mi je on rekao,

507
00:17:58,580 --> 00:17:59,860
 pa znaš,

508
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:02,220
 ja ti svake godine idem za badnje k svojim roditeljima,

509
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:03,780
 i uvijek sam na misi sa obitelji,

510
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:04,880
 sad mi to užasno fali,

511
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:05,360
 sam sam,

512
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,440
 nisam mogla zbog posla,

513
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:08,000
 odleti dobiti leti,

514
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:08,380
 ili šta li,

515
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:09,100
 već ne sjećam se,

516
00:18:09,100 --> 00:18:09,860
 to je bilo davno,

517
00:18:09,860 --> 00:18:11,340
 i mene onako,

518
00:18:11,340 --> 00:18:13,020
 kako sam empata po prirodi,

519
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:13,640
 ja sam,

520
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:14,800
 meni bilo žao,

521
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:15,440
 ja sam rekla,

522
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:15,820
 ok,

523
00:18:15,820 --> 00:18:17,020
 idem ja s tobom,

524
00:18:17,020 --> 00:18:17,640
 ali kako ću,

525
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:17,920
 kažem,

526
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:18,540
 preveze,

527
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:21,020
 i sad ja ulazim u crkvu,

528
00:18:21,020 --> 00:18:22,360
 onajku bučeno štikle,

529
00:18:22,360 --> 00:18:23,040
 ono haljena,

530
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:25,040
 buči se tam dva metra bundica,

531
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:26,340
 bijela od janjeta,

532
00:18:26,340 --> 00:18:26,820
 ono,

533
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:28,260
 i oni,

534
00:18:28,260 --> 00:18:29,300
 scena,

535
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:29,700
 ono,

536
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:30,880
 i sad svi se okreću,

537
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:31,520
 kao gledaju,

538
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:32,080
 oni vjeruju,

539
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:33,300
 ja sama sebi ne vjerujem,

540
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:34,340
 šta ja radim ovdje,

541
00:18:34,340 --> 00:18:36,080
 ali prva pjesma,

542
00:18:36,080 --> 00:18:37,020
 ono,

543
00:18:37,020 --> 00:18:38,080
 baš neka snažna,

544
00:18:38,080 --> 00:18:38,580
 snažna,

545
00:18:38,580 --> 00:18:38,760
 ono,

546
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:40,040
 muzika i tako,

547
00:18:40,040 --> 00:18:40,620
 ova kapela,

548
00:18:40,620 --> 00:18:42,240
 kako su pjevali me nešto tu,

549
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,020
 neke osjeće,

550
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:43,280
 ono,

551
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:45,140
 neke emocije,

552
00:18:45,320 --> 00:18:45,760
 jednostavno,

553
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:46,040
 ne znam,

554
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:46,880
 neko ganuće,

555
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:49,220
 nešto preneobično,

556
00:18:49,220 --> 00:18:51,840
 i onda sečanik krene pričat,

557
00:18:51,840 --> 00:18:53,660
 Bog je rođen za ljubav,

558
00:18:53,660 --> 00:18:55,480
 on je rođen da vi budete sretni,

559
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,600
 on se je rodio za vas,

560
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:57,720
 i ja počnem plakat,

561
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:58,580
 ne znam šta mi je,

562
00:18:58,580 --> 00:18:59,840
 on me gleda,

563
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:00,920
 i onako mi stišće ruku,

564
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:02,260
 sjećam se te scene,

565
00:19:02,260 --> 00:19:02,960
 ja ne mogu,

566
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:03,160
 ono,

567
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,300
 kontrolirati te suze,

568
00:19:04,300 --> 00:19:04,580
 znači,

569
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:05,920
 to je curelo iz mene,

570
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:06,600
 ko iz kabla,

571
00:19:06,600 --> 00:19:06,780
 ono,

572
00:19:06,780 --> 00:19:08,220
 šminkuću si pokvalit,

573
00:19:08,220 --> 00:19:09,120
 kao ne,

574
00:19:09,120 --> 00:19:10,300
 ali nije me bilo brigo,

575
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:10,660
 iskreno,

576
00:19:10,660 --> 00:19:11,820
 ja sam se tu isplakala,

577
00:19:11,820 --> 00:19:14,780
 i onda je bila trenutak prve pričasti,

578
00:19:14,780 --> 00:19:16,220
 i ja sam morala stati u taj red,

579
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:17,260
 znam da nisam smijela,

580
00:19:17,260 --> 00:19:18,280
 i da sam živjela u grijehu,

581
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:20,180
 i da se svi mi moramo prvo ispovijediti,

582
00:19:20,180 --> 00:19:22,760
 nego što idemo ovoga na setu pričast,

583
00:19:22,760 --> 00:19:23,860
 ali to je bilo zjače od mene,

584
00:19:23,860 --> 00:19:25,600
 mislim da je ta od Isus mene snažno pozva,

585
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:25,980
 rekao ono,

586
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:26,420
 daj više,

587
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:27,480
 pogledaj u mene,

588
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:27,820
 ono,

589
00:19:27,820 --> 00:19:29,120
 skreni svoj pogled,

590
00:19:29,120 --> 00:19:29,760
 ja sam tu,

591
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:31,080
 želim te slobodnu,

592
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:32,680
 i nakon toga,

593
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,800
 ja sam pet dana kasnije,

594
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:36,200
 znači nakon nove godine,

595
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,120
 sjedla u svom stanu,

596
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:40,140
 i osjedla u nutrini,

597
00:19:40,140 --> 00:19:41,780
 ja moram otići,

598
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:43,860
 ako odem na snimanje u Kanadu,

599
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:45,660
 i poslije se preselim u Australiju,

600
00:19:45,660 --> 00:19:46,980
 za koju sam već imala vizu,

601
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:48,560
 nešto će se loše desiti,

602
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:49,640
 znači ne, ne, ne, ja,

603
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:52,540
 ja sam ostavila pola stvari u stanu,

604
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:53,900
 skupila onak dva kofera,

605
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:55,120
 ostavila stan,

606
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:57,580
 baš sam neki dan razmišljala znakovito,

607
00:19:57,580 --> 00:19:59,120
 ja sam krenula za Isusom,

608
00:19:59,120 --> 00:19:59,980
 napustila sve,

609
00:19:59,980 --> 00:20:02,160
 ja nisam ni znala da ja zapravo krećem za njime,

610
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,480
 nisam ni znala da me on opće pozvao,

611
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:04,120
 ali me pozvao,

612
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:06,040
 i ja sam došla ljepo u Zagreb,

613
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:07,760
 i umjesto na snimanje,

614
00:20:07,760 --> 00:20:09,420
 ja otišla u Vinogradsku bolnicu,

615
00:20:09,420 --> 00:20:10,580
 i prijavila se na odjel,

616
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:12,260
 tako da,

617
00:20:12,260 --> 00:20:14,060
 profesor sako man je ostao u šoku,

618
00:20:14,060 --> 00:20:14,740
 kad me je vidio,

619
00:20:14,740 --> 00:20:15,760
 kao, kaj si ti je došla,

620
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:17,220
 kažem, da, da, da, treba malo ovoga,

621
00:20:17,220 --> 00:20:18,300
 nisam baš dobro,

622
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:19,880
 i ta ruka, ono, me zezza,

623
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:20,580
 sad kao,

624
00:20:20,580 --> 00:20:22,080
 ja sam to sve onako uljepšavala,

625
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,000
 sama sebi sam,

626
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:24,820
 si bila prejadna,

627
00:20:24,820 --> 00:20:26,740
 ostala u bolnici,

628
00:20:32,240 --> 00:20:34,080
 baš susret sa živim Bogom,

629
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:34,940
 kada je bilo

630
00:20:34,940 --> 00:20:36,860
 Međunarodni dan Bolesnika,

631
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:37,660
 Gospa Lurcka,

632
00:20:37,660 --> 00:20:40,000
 došli su nam časne sestre

633
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:40,840
 pričati o Bogu,

634
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:41,700
 o tome da nakon

635
00:20:41,700 --> 00:20:43,120
 bolničkog liječenja,

636
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:43,880
 mi svi trebamo

637
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,020
 krenuti put zajednice,

638
00:20:45,020 --> 00:20:46,220
 ali i vjerske zajednice,

639
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:47,780
 i tako su nam pričale o Bogu,

640
00:20:47,780 --> 00:20:49,120
 i bila jedna mlada časna

641
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:49,700
 pored mene,

642
00:20:49,700 --> 00:20:50,880
 koja šnije obukla veo,

643
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:51,960
 znači novici Jatkinja,

644
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:52,880
 ja sam isto ridala,

645
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:53,520
 i plakala,

646
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:55,240
 i dala mi je krunicu,

647
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,340
 i stisnula mi ruku,

648
00:20:57,900 --> 00:20:59,080
 i one su otišle,

649
00:20:59,080 --> 00:21:00,520
 i ja sam drugi dan

650
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:01,640
 imala baš onak neke

651
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,940
 predepresivne misli,

652
00:21:02,940 --> 00:21:03,720
 ono, došlo mi je,

653
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:05,200
 šta sam napravila,

654
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,560
 otišla sam iz Amerike,

655
00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:08,000
 prijavila sam se u bolnicu,

656
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:09,000
 sad će se vi znati,

657
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:10,640
 ako to izađe negdje u novinama,

658
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:11,400
 ako objave,

659
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:13,320
 ono, ona je ovisnica,

660
00:21:13,320 --> 00:21:14,080
 pa šta će,

661
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:14,380
 mislim,

662
00:21:14,380 --> 00:21:15,680
 a ja sam to viješto skrivala,

663
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:15,940
 ali ono,

664
00:21:15,940 --> 00:21:17,060
 nisem mogla kužit na meni,

665
00:21:17,060 --> 00:21:17,680
 ja sam bila ono,

666
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:18,520
 kao finjak, ne,

667
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:20,960
 i onak,

668
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,020
 ne mogu,

669
00:21:22,020 --> 00:21:23,100
 ja ne mogu iću zajednicu,

670
00:21:23,140 --> 00:21:23,880
 kao ćeš u zajednicu,

671
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:24,800
 pa ne znam biti normalna,

672
00:21:24,800 --> 00:21:26,140
 ono, ja sam manekenka,

673
00:21:26,140 --> 00:21:26,720
 mislim, ono,

674
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,120
 imala sam šofera,

675
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:29,600
 jela sam po restoranima,

676
00:21:29,600 --> 00:21:30,680
 nisam prava ni tveš,

677
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:31,420
 mislim, ne samo to,

678
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:32,320
 nego ja nisam radila,

679
00:21:32,320 --> 00:21:33,380
 znači, moj posao je bio,

680
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:34,920
 da, ono,

681
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:35,680
 smješkaj se,

682
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:36,400
 budi izgodna,

683
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,720
 lijepa, mršava, vitka,

684
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,140
 i to je to, ne,

685
00:21:39,140 --> 00:21:40,860
 ne, kad sam si tako pomišlao,

686
00:21:40,860 --> 00:21:41,420
 sam rekla, pa ne,

687
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:42,340
 ja to ne mogu,

688
00:21:42,340 --> 00:21:43,320
 šta sam sad napravila,

689
00:21:43,320 --> 00:21:43,800
 znači, ono,

690
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:44,780
 šta sam napravila?

691
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:47,100
 I tada još nisu bile rešetke

692
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:47,760
 na prozorima,

693
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:49,260
 evo, kao što ovdje imamo,

694
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:51,100
 ja sam tako sjedla na prozoru,

695
00:21:51,100 --> 00:21:52,180
 tad sam bila još pušač

696
00:21:52,180 --> 00:21:53,460
 i, ono, pušla tu cigaretu

697
00:21:53,460 --> 00:21:54,580
 i, ono, pogledala gore

698
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:54,900
 i rekla,

699
00:21:54,900 --> 00:21:55,920
 Božak, ti postojiš,

700
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,840
 ja još uvijek nisam sigurna

701
00:21:56,840 --> 00:21:57,500
 ali ti postojiš,

702
00:21:57,500 --> 00:21:58,880
 ko si ti ili tebe ima, nema,

703
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:01,200
 onda napravi sad jedno čudo,

704
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,140
 spasi me,

705
00:22:02,140 --> 00:22:03,300
 napravi nešto,

706
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:04,640
 jer ja ću sad se baciti,

707
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,220
 jer tako je,

708
00:22:05,220 --> 00:22:05,620
 lakše,

709
00:22:05,620 --> 00:22:07,780
 jednostavno pobići od svih tih problema,

710
00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:08,800
 jednostavno ne vidim,

711
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:10,160
 opće da imam snage

712
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,960
 za preživiti još jedan dan u bolnici,

713
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:12,960
 a kam li se mijenjati,

714
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:13,340
 ili ne znam,

715
00:22:13,340 --> 00:22:15,580
 ići putem u neku zajednicu za Bogom,

716
00:22:15,580 --> 00:22:17,740
