 neću ja tu dugo ostati,

967
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,780
 znači ja sam si to mislila,

968
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:35,420
 onda način života,

969
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:37,520
 znači princip odnosno duhovne zajednice,

970
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:38,280
 orajt labora,

971
00:28:38,280 --> 00:28:39,320
 znači radi molitva,

972
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:40,600
 tamo se samo moli

973
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:41,960
 i samo se radi,

974
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:43,880
 jer rad nas pašava,

975
00:28:43,880 --> 00:28:45,460
 daje nam smisla o nekom životu,

976
00:28:45,460 --> 00:28:47,380
 pogotovo kad ti vidiš plodove svoga rada,

977
00:28:47,380 --> 00:28:49,760
 a molitva nas približava Bogu

978
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:51,500
 i uvodi u jedan taj duhovni set

979
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:55,360
 i život tamo je vrlo drugačiji od života

980
00:28:55,360 --> 00:28:56,000
 i ljudi vani,

981
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,760
 zato što je poprilično redovnički,

982
00:28:57,760 --> 00:28:59,320
 znači živi se u bratovištinama,

983
00:28:59,320 --> 00:28:59,980
 ko ne znaje,

984
00:28:59,980 --> 00:29:01,240
 evo ako nekog možda zanima,

985
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,260
 cure žive same,

986
00:29:02,260 --> 00:29:03,660
 odnosno u zasebnima,

987
00:29:03,660 --> 00:29:05,800
 muškarci su u muškim bratovištinama,

988
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:07,880
 buđen je u šest u jutro,

989
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:10,200
 u pola sedam se ide nakon toalete,

990
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,060
 odmah u kapelu,

991
00:29:11,060 --> 00:29:13,240
 znači prva stvar u jutro je pozdrav Isusu,

992
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:14,320
 molitvom krunice,

993
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:17,240
 ispred presvetog oltarskog sankramenta,

994
00:29:17,340 --> 00:29:20,040
 znači otvorimo i tu molimo našu jutrnju krunicu prvu,

995
00:29:20,040 --> 00:29:21,140
 radosna otajstva,

996
00:29:21,140 --> 00:29:23,720
 onda je parola didio,

997
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:25,380
 znači riječ Božja se komentira

998
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:27,280
 i tu se već dijeli ono šta živiš

999
00:29:27,280 --> 00:29:28,240
 i tu je meni bilo onak,

1000
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:30,560
 zna kaj one pričaju istinu o sebi,

1001
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:32,380
 ono kaj one stvarno žive,

1002
00:29:32,380 --> 00:29:32,860
 ova priča,

1003
00:29:32,860 --> 00:29:33,660
 ja sam usudila,

1004
00:29:33,660 --> 00:29:35,180
 pritao oprost ovu,

1005
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:36,960
 ja sam tebe loše vidjela,

1006
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:38,640
 i uče si mi digla živce ovo ono.

1007
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:40,500
 U osam ujutro počinje posao,

1008
00:29:40,500 --> 00:29:41,380
 radi se u paru,

1009
00:29:41,380 --> 00:29:43,040
 uvijek jedna ima svog Anđela Čuvara,

1010
00:29:43,040 --> 00:29:45,040
 to je starija djevađa koja se brine za nju,

1011
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:47,940
 dok je ona na samom početku uvodi u pravila

1012
00:29:47,940 --> 00:29:49,180
 i sad kako se živi to.

1013
00:29:49,180 --> 00:29:51,580
 Slobodno vrijeme,

1014
00:29:51,580 --> 00:29:52,560
 iza ručka,

1015
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:53,740
 onda se opet radi,

1016
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:55,460
 moli se druga krunica na poslu,

1017
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:56,960
 onda se moli milosrdno u tri

1018
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,900
 i zadnja krunica na kraju dana

1019
00:29:58,900 --> 00:30:00,500
 nakon posla u kapelici,

1020
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:01,780
 znači ovoga,

1021
00:30:01,780 --> 00:30:03,140
 mole se tri krunice dnevno,

1022
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:04,160
 milosrdna krunica,

1023
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:08,520
 da, znači, ali to je potrebno,

1024
00:30:08,520 --> 00:30:09,740
 jer kad ti živiš u zlu,

1025
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:11,160
 kad si toliko u zlu,

1026
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:12,760
 znači ja nisam bila onak mala u zlu,

1027
00:30:12,760 --> 00:30:14,220
 ja sam bila jako u zlu, jel?

1028
00:30:14,220 --> 00:30:15,340
 Važno je,

1029
00:30:15,340 --> 00:30:16,880
 Majka Elvira je rekla da su tri krunice

1030
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:17,780
 jednake egzorcizmu

1031
00:30:17,780 --> 00:30:18,920
 i da moramo puno moliti,

1032
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:20,860
 zato što smo bile jako u velikom zlu

1033
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:22,740
 i da je potrebno da mi nadođemo

1034
00:30:22,740 --> 00:30:26,140
 i da uopće se to svjetlo ukaže nama na putu,

1035
00:30:26,140 --> 00:30:28,600
 obzirom okolnosti kako smo živjele.

1036
00:30:28,600 --> 00:30:31,580
 I u početku je to meni sve bilo onak kao

1037
00:30:31,580 --> 00:30:32,920
 previše, previše, previše

1038
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:34,400
 i nisam baš ono ništa osjećala,

1039
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:35,600
 si stajala bi pred tim,

1040
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:37,600
 odnosno klećala pred presvjetim,

1041
00:30:37,600 --> 00:30:39,280
 nisam osjećala

1042
00:30:39,280 --> 00:30:40,920
 i rekli su mi savjeti,

1043
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:41,740
 ti samo budi,

1044
00:30:41,740 --> 00:30:42,720
 mi ćemo moliti za tebe

1045
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:44,180
 i samo pusti Isusa da uđe,

1046
00:30:44,180 --> 00:30:44,900
 di da uđe,

1047
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:46,020
 ne kužim ono,

1048
00:30:46,020 --> 00:30:47,060
 kak da uđe,

1049
00:30:47,060 --> 00:30:48,180
 nisam ništa to kužila,

1050
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:49,940
 dok onda jednog dana,

1051
00:30:49,940 --> 00:30:52,020
 malo po malo se oči te duše

1052
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:53,480
 su se počele otvarati

1053
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:55,040
 i jednostavno onda je polako

1054
00:30:55,040 --> 00:30:57,200
 iz mjeseca u mjesec

1055
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:58,540
 se duša počela buditi

1056
00:30:58,540 --> 00:30:59,420
 i to duhovno,

1057
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:01,460
 a ovo tijelo se počelo smanjivati

1058
00:31:01,460 --> 00:31:01,980
 što je super

1059
00:31:01,980 --> 00:31:03,120
 i to je bila velika promjena,

1060
00:31:03,120 --> 00:31:04,480
 ali ja sam još uvijek bila

1061
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:06,020
 jako fokusirana na svoj izgled,

1062
00:31:06,020 --> 00:31:06,660
 to ću reći samo

1063
00:31:06,660 --> 00:31:07,520
 u kratkim crtama

1064
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:08,400
 i stalno sam se gledala

1065
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:08,920
 ovo gledalo

1066
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:10,120
 i ovo sam se malo izdebljala,

1067
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:11,040
 prestala pušiti,

1068
00:31:11,040 --> 00:31:12,040
 tam se fino papa

1069
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:12,800
 i to sve

1070
00:31:12,800 --> 00:31:15,720
 i počele su mi rast akne,

1071
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:17,040
 to je počela sam imati

1072
00:31:17,040 --> 00:31:18,040
 jako velikih problema

1073
00:31:18,040 --> 00:31:19,420
 sa kožama

1074
00:31:19,420 --> 00:31:20,080
 jer ja sam cijelo vrijeme

1075
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:20,940
 mislila ja ću sad,

1076
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:21,840
 sad ću otići,

1077
00:31:21,900 --> 00:31:23,000
 uđuću mjesecu ću otići,

1078
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:23,580
 prikinuću

1079
00:31:23,580 --> 00:31:24,220
 i ne mogu više

1080
00:31:24,220 --> 00:31:25,360
 preteško mi je ne vidim

1081
00:31:25,360 --> 00:31:26,500
 kako ću se promijeniti,

1082
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:27,760
 ko će sad tu biti tri godine

1083
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:28,040
 i ono,

1084
00:31:28,040 --> 00:31:28,840
 nemam ja vremena,

1085
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:31,200
 nemam ja ne znam kojeg posla,

1086
00:31:31,200 --> 00:31:32,600
 ali ne mogu ja sad tu biti,

1087
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:33,200
 uglavnom sam znamo

1088
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:33,700
 gdje bi išla,

1089
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:34,660
 ali kao ne bi ja tu bila.

1090
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:35,720
 Međutim,

1091
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:37,440
 ja sam toliko akne velike

1092
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:39,160
 dobila po licu,

1093
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:40,680
 po čelu,

1094
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:41,360
 po vratu,

1095
00:31:41,360 --> 00:31:41,840
 po svuda,

1096
00:31:41,840 --> 00:31:43,160
 da ja od srama,

1097
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,340
 kako će ja sad takva

1098
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:45,280
 izaći u javnosti

1099
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:46,100
 da me neko vidi.

1100
00:31:46,100 --> 00:31:48,700
 Ja sam ovoga odlučila,

1101
00:31:48,700 --> 00:31:49,480
 ja ću ostati,

1102
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:50,500
 ali to je bilo isto

1103
00:31:50,500 --> 00:31:51,260
 jako značajno,

1104
00:31:51,260 --> 00:31:52,560
 jer više se nisam tako rado

1105
00:31:52,560 --> 00:31:53,620
 ogledala u ogledalu,

1106
00:31:53,620 --> 00:31:55,160
 nego je gospodin time

1107
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:57,080
 preusmjerio moj pogled

1108
00:31:57,080 --> 00:31:57,600
 na njega,

1109
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,220
 jer sam prestala gledati sebe,

1110
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:00,720
 jer sam pribila samo,

1111
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,620
 fokusila na sebe,

1112
00:32:01,620 --> 00:32:03,240
 počela sam gledati gospodina.

1113
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,960
 Iskoristio dvije muhe,

1114
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:05,720
 jednu mudarca.

1115
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:08,500
 Tako, jako je mudar

1116
00:32:08,500 --> 00:32:09,480
 i dosjetljiv,

1117
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:11,120
 kako privući,

1118
00:32:11,120 --> 00:32:13,320
 ali meni je poslužio se time,

1119
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:14,860
 i tako sam ja krenula

1120
00:32:14,860 --> 00:32:16,920
 upoznavati Isusa

1121
00:32:16,920 --> 00:32:18,040
 i ozdravljati

1122
00:32:18,040 --> 00:32:18,860
 i plakati

1123
00:32:18,860 --> 00:32:20,220
 i vidjeti sve te situacije

1124
00:32:20,220 --> 00:32:21,060
 koje sam prošla,

1125
00:32:21,060 --> 00:32:22,700
 bolne odrastave roditelja,

1126
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:24,380
 moje rano djetinstvo,

1127
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:25,400
 kasnije neuspjehe

1128
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,940
 i neke stvari druge u životu

1129
00:32:26,940 --> 00:32:28,560
 koje su me jako ranile.

1130
00:32:28,560 --> 00:32:29,780
 Vidjela sam sve svoje rane

1131
00:32:29,780 --> 00:32:30,840
 i vidim ih još dan danas,

1132
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:31,240
 ali eto,

1133
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,320
 tada je bilo baš ono,

1134
00:32:32,320 --> 00:32:34,720
 počela su mi se otvarati

1135
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:35,600
 oči duše

1136
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:36,760
 i duhovnog života

1137
00:32:36,760 --> 00:32:38,640
 i jednostavno zaljubila sam se

1138
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:39,880
 u taj način života

1139
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:40,420
 i Isusa

1140
00:32:40,420 --> 00:32:43,620
 zato što sam počela živjeti za druge,

1141
00:32:43,620 --> 00:32:45,460
 a ne više za sebe.

1142
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,620
 shvatila da živiš za druge,

1143
00:32:47,620 --> 00:32:48,360
 kad nekog drugog,

1144
00:32:48,360 --> 00:32:50,080
 svoju sestru stavim na prvo mjesto,

1145
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:50,960
 što to znači,

1146
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:52,720
 možda na koji način

1147
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:54,620
 ta molitva na koljenima

1148
00:32:54,620 --> 00:32:55,480
 koju smo mi molili

1149
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:57,460
 je postala konkretan život.

1150
00:32:57,460 --> 00:32:58,500
 Znači, moliš krunicu,

1151
00:32:58,500 --> 00:32:59,300
 uklanjaš se i sve,

1152
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:00,520
 ali onda na poslu,

1153
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:00,800
 ne znam,

1154
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:01,720
 nekome je teško,

1155
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,980
 ti odradiš njen posao,

1156
00:33:02,980 --> 00:33:03,660
 neko, ne znam,

1157
00:33:03,660 --> 00:33:05,900
 zaužinu i njen najdrži kolač,

1158
00:33:05,900 --> 00:33:06,920
 ja ću joj dati svoj,

1159
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:08,580
 zato što želim da ona bude sretna

1160
00:33:08,580 --> 00:33:09,360
 ili nekom ću,

1161
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:12,260
 zato što želim nekog razveselit,

1162
00:33:12,260 --> 00:33:13,980
 napraviti krevet ili oprat veš,

1163
00:33:13,980 --> 00:33:14,960
 ili tako neke stvari.

1164
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:16,760
 Znači, gledat potrebe drugog,

1165
00:33:16,760 --> 00:33:19,060
 a ne gledat potrebe svoje i sebe.

1166
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:20,420
 I to je nešto bilo...

1167
00:33:20,420 --> 00:33:21,320
 To je značena promjena.

1168
00:33:21,320 --> 00:33:23,020
 Da, to je bilo onak nešto predivno.

1169
00:33:23,020 --> 00:33:24,940
 Ja sam shvatila da je to puno ljepše

1170
00:33:24,940 --> 00:33:25,640
 nego kad sam prije,

1171
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:27,160
 ono, mislila samo na svoje potrebe,

1172
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,800
 ja bi, ja bi, meni, meni, meni,

1173
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:30,880
 a zapravo nisam primjećivala druge

1174
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:32,560
 i možda sam ih i materialnim stvarima

1175
00:33:32,560 --> 00:33:35,080
 pokušala nagraditi ili iskazati svoju ljubav.

1176
00:33:35,080 --> 00:33:38,560
 I ovdje sam, doživivši tu molitvu

1177
00:33:38,560 --> 00:33:40,160
 u konkretnom životu,

1178
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:41,920
 živeći to evanđelje Isusovo,

1179
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:43,480
 zapravo otkrila,

1180
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:46,300
 pa ja želim svoj život od sada

1181
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:48,740
 živjeti kvalitetno

1182
00:33:48,740 --> 00:33:50,240
 i želim ga darovati Isusu

1183
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:52,760
 onako kako On želi da ja živim.

1184
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:54,320
 Kao posliječen način života.

1185
00:33:54,320 --> 00:33:55,460
 Pa je, zapravo da.

1186
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:57,600
 Jer tu se ta počela rađati ljubav

1187
00:33:57,600 --> 00:33:58,940
 da živim za drugi,

1188
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:00,480
 da ne živim više samo za sebe.

1189
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:02,020
 I onda mi je, evo,

1190
00:34:02,100 --> 00:34:03,560
 kod nas u zajednici postoje

1191
00:34:03,560 --> 00:34:05,260
 i časne sestre,

1192
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:07,500
 znači taj red i red svećenika

1193
00:34:07,500 --> 00:34:08,720
 ili posvećene braće.

1194
00:34:08,720 --> 00:34:10,920
 I ja sam počela prvo razmišljati,

1195
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,240
 onda sam ih stavila u molitvu

1196
00:34:12,240 --> 00:34:14,100
 da bih i ja isto se posvetila

1197
00:34:14,100 --> 00:34:15,360
 i živjela za Isusa,

1198
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:17,420
 odnosno služila toj dječici

1199
00:34:17,420 --> 00:34:18,860
 koja su u misijskim kućama

1200
00:34:18,860 --> 00:34:20,000
 kao časna sestra.

1201
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,940
 I krenula se moliti

1202
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:24,220
 na tu, neću reći nakon,

1203
00:34:24,220 --> 00:34:25,860
 ali sam počela Isusu govoriti

1204
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:26,780
 ono računaj na mene,

1205
00:34:26,780 --> 00:34:27,740
 koristi moje ruke,

1206
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:29,640
 moje tijelo, moje zagrljaje.

1207
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:31,880
 Želim toj djeci biti majka duhovna,

1208
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:32,600
 ali neka djeca,

1209
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:34,180
 ta, u misijskim kućama,

1210
00:34:34,180 --> 00:34:36,620
 su upravo došla u zajednicu čenako,

1211
00:34:36,620 --> 00:34:38,180
 ali možda su im roditelji umrli

1212
00:34:38,180 --> 00:34:40,100
 od hiva ili od neke ovisnosti

1213
00:34:40,100 --> 00:34:40,900
